PRIVACY POLICY

Effective Date: May 5, 2025

This Privacy Policy explains how Sign House Inc. ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses, and protects your information when you use the Nexus Lite Connector application.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect information including your name, company name, email, and accounting-related data as necessary to operate the app and integrate with QuickBooks.

2. How We Use Your Information
We use your information solely to provide and improve our services, including but not limited to:
- Creating estimates in QuickBooks;
- Troubleshooting issues;
- Complying with applicable laws.

3. Data Sharing
We do not sell or share your information with third parties, except as required to integrate with QuickBooks or comply with legal obligations.

4. Data Storage
Your data is stored securely. We take reasonable measures to protect it from unauthorized access.

5. Your Rights
You may request to view, correct, or delete your data at any time by contacting us.

6. Third-Party Services
Our app integrates with Intuit QuickBooks. Their privacy policy also applies. Please review it at: https://quickbooks.intuit.com/ca/privacy-policy/

7. Changes
We may update this policy. Continued use of the app means you accept the new terms.

Contact: info@signhouse.ca
